{
  "stem": "15962.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we decided to stay one more night and only go out of the camp the following day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was, to my recollection, May 5.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what we have learned later is that they had orders to lock us all up in barracks and set fire to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the order from the Gestapo, from the higher up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the commander apparently was negotiating with the American troops that were closing in and exchanged his so-called freedom for not setting fire to the-- to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they put up a white flag, piled into some trucks, and drove who knows where.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so all of a sudden, there was just the--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just the prisoners were left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And again, there was the contrast between many of the Hungarian Jews who haven't been two or three years in concentration camps, so they were in much better physical condition, and even some of them still had some food that they brought with you, not much.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also had reasonable clothes that they were wearing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was a-- a distinction between what the endurance that was left in human beings that played a role in survival.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think we were one of the small exceptions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most of them were Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these were both men and women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 15.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
